				<a href="#donate" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold no-underline transition-all duration-200" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); background-color: #FFD9E0; color: #4A4A4A; border-radius: 8px;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.92'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">Become a Monthly Partner →</a>
