				<img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/8b5d1c39f892218c978d3e3caf5720e09833bbc4-1024x1024.png?w=800&auto=format" alt="Scripture in the city" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
				<img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/65bfbb03bafd33cde3ec1fc7898e45bd59cdd3d5-4912x3264.jpg?w=800&auto=format" alt="Sharing the Father's heart" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
